AES is vulnerable to its mode: ECB
u can use the cipher as Oracles to check if ur encrypted chosen plaintext is equal to the encrypted flag
just work char-by-char and check if the result string is equal to the oracles output
recvuntil() works perfectly in this case to extract what we need

